metadata.name: Seedling #1
metadata.description:
A collection of up to 10,000 unique, magical Seedlings growing on the Ethereum Blockchain.

Utility-enabled and rarity-powered.

50% of royalties from secondary sales go into the Harvest Pool. Cultivators (holders) can plant seedlings to harvest rewards.

Decentralization and longevity are at the heart of Seedlings NFT. A community-driven future with a foundation built on immutable smart contracts and a convenient dApp hosted on IPFS. 

Cultivators hold full commercial rights to their Seedlings.
